      "content": "{\n  \"layout\": {\n    \"Umbraco.BlockList\": [\n      {\n        \"contentUdi\": \"umb://element/8b7c66eadaa74d44808699dba9277d48\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"contentUdi\": \"umb://element/cf19042b96814273b5a9beb01e6b2fab\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"contentUdi\": \"umb://element/c27ff6d4cc8746dfa9dc55b27da5931d\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"contentUdi\": \"umb://element/0dea641722e84c489c17f532fb7640ba\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"contentUdi\": \"umb://element/deb52737788245e0ac88724544bfc1f4\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"contentUdi\": \"umb://element/c5aaa9203c8a41c8ac6aca162ca43cd4\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"contentUdi\": \"umb://element/cd96b0e20fda42c8953c8acf60fd9add\"\n      }\n    ]\n  },\n  \"contentData\": [\n    {\n      \"contentTypeKey\": \"48cee39d-6ba9-4599-b547-147a9bb31a82\",\n      \"udi\": \"umb://element/8b7c66eadaa74d44808699dba9277d48\",\n      \"textbox\": \"<p class=\\\"s3\\\">We've combined the best of both worlds into a single, powerful programme. We aim to give staff access to:</p>\\n<div class=\\\"s6\\\">\\n<ul>\\n<li>Internal and external expertise: staff can tap into a diverse pool of coaches and mentors, both within our organisation and through our external partnerships.</li>\\n<li>Coaching elements in management fundamentals: we empower staff to enhance their leadership skills with coaching components integrated into this core development programme.</li>\\n</ul>\\n</div>\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"contentTypeKey\": \"48cee39d-6ba9-4599-b547-147a9bb31a82\",\n      \"udi\": \"umb://element/cf19042b96814273b5a9beb01e6b2fab\",\n      \"textbox\": \"<h3 class=\\\"s3\\\">Coaching vs. Mentoring: Tailored Support</h3>\\n<p class=\\\"s3\\\">We understand that the needs of our colleagues may vary over time. That's why we offer both coaching and mentoring. But what's the difference between the two you might ask? This is our take: </p>\\n<ul>\\n<li class=\\\"s3\\\">Coaching: a focus on specific skill development, behavioural shifts, and performance enhancement. It's typically shorter-term and goal-oriented.</li>\\n<li class=\\\"s3\\\">Mentoring: this emphasises broader career and personal development guided by the mentor's experience. This relationship tends to be longer-term.</li>\\n</ul>\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"contentTypeKey\": \"48cee39d-6ba9-4599-b547-147a9bb31a82\",\n      \"udi\": \"umb://element/c27ff6d4cc8746dfa9dc55b27da5931d\",\n      \"textbox\": \"<h3>What does our programme offer for both mentees and mentors?</h3>\\n<p>Our coaching and mentoring programme delivers advantages for mentees and mentors and the organisation as a whole. Let's take a look:</p>\\n<p><strong>Mentees</strong></p>\\n<ul>\\n<li>Gain fresh perspectives for innovative problem-solving.</li>\\n<li>Develop essential skills, boosting confidence and competence.</li>\\n<li>Receive personalised guidance for continuous growth.</li>\\n<li>Benefit from accountability and support in realising your goals.</li>\\n</ul>\\n<p><strong>Mentors/Coaches</strong></p>\\n<ul>\\n<li>Expand your leadership and coaching abilities.</li>\\n<li>Gain recognition as subject matter experts.</li>\\n<li>Share your knowledge, giving back to the organisation.</li>\\n<li>Experience the fulfilling rewards of helping others thrive.</li>\\n</ul>\\n<p><strong>Our organisation</strong></p>\\n<ul>\\n<li>Increased employee engagement, performance, and retention.</li>\\n<li>A deep commitment to a culture of continuous learning</li>\\n<li>Enhanced sense of responsibility for personal and professional growth</li>\\n<li>Improved mental well-being among all team members.</li>\\n</ul>\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"contentTypeKey\": \"48cee39d-6ba9-4599-b547-147a9bb31a82\",\n      \"udi\": \"umb://element/0dea641722e84c489c17f532fb7640ba\",\n      \"textbox\": \"<h3>What would I use a mentor for?</h3>\\n<p>This is far from an exhaustive process and it is completely down to the individual as you identify where you need support and advice.</p>\\n<p>But we think there are some brilliant topics to explore. Perhaps you could work with your mentor or coach on topics like</p>\\n<ul>\\n<li>Smoothly transitioning into new roles, teams, or projects</li>\\n<li>Optimising time management, prioritisation, and relationships</li>\\n<li>Finding better work-life balance</li>\\n<li>Overcoming barriers and building confidence</li>\\n<li>Returning to work after an extended absence</li>\\n<li>Maximising your role in multi-partnership or cross-team settings</li>\\n</ul>\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"contentTypeKey\": \"48cee39d-6ba9-4599-b547-147a9bb31a82\",\n      \"udi\": \"umb://element/deb52737788245e0ac88724544bfc1f4\",\n      \"textbox\": \"<h3 class=\\\"s3\\\">Where do I get started? </h3>\\n<p>We encourage our staff to discuss this with your line managers. Share your interests and get their support. This is also something you can do with if you're reading this from outside the WMCA. </p>\\n<div class=\\\"s6\\\">We have a Matching Hub internally that helps colleagues select a mentor or coach based on your unique needs.</div>\\n<div class=\\\"s6\\\"></div>\\n<div class=\\\"s6\\\">And over time you may wish to explore Reverse Mentoring where you make it a two-way learning process to share fresh insights.</div>\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"contentTypeKey\": \"48cee39d-6ba9-4599-b547-147a9bb31a82\",\n      \"udi\": \"umb://element/c5aaa9203c8a41c8ac6aca162ca43cd4\",\n      \"textbox\": \"<h3>What learning opportunities do you offer to staff?</h3>\\n<p class=\\\"s3\\\">A big part of life at the WMCA is about supporting continuous learning.</p>\\n<p class=\\\"s3\\\">We offer colleagues resources to empower your growth journey:</p>\\n<div class=\\\"s6\\\">This includes an introduction to coaching through our eLearning pool. We offer management fundamentals courses and provide informative documents and checklists/models to work to.</div>\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"contentTypeKey\": \"48cee39d-6ba9-4599-b547-147a9bb31a82\",\n      \"udi\": \"umb://element/cd96b0e20fda42c8953c8acf60fd9add\",\n      \"textbox\": \"<p>Please remember that you can learn more about <a href=\\\"https://www.wmca.org.uk/careers-at-the-wmca/\\\">careers at West Midlands Combined Authority</a> here.</p>\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"settingsData\": []\n}",
