    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[As a learning organisation, we're deeply invested in personal and professional growth.

That's why we've created a dynamic coaching and mentoring culture here at West Midlands Combined Authority, offering a blended approach to development that goes beyond traditional training.]]></Value>
